title: The Golden Age (Angel of Midheaven)
summary: The Golden Age (Angel of Midheaven) Ban Suho, a guard who died after failing to protect the Princess from the assassins! Back in time two years with an unknown force!“ This time, I must…”Determined to protect the Princess this time and he sets out in search of the sealed power to become stronger. Indeed Ban Suho gains the power from an unknown force. Will he be able to protect the Princess? Jungchonsuwolryong The Golden Age 중천수월령
